Package: rKenya
Type: Package
Title: Kenya Maps: Counties and Sub-Counties for Spatial Visualization
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Kilai Mutua, PhD",
      email = "samkmutua@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides spatial boundary data for Kenya at the county and
    sub-county administrative levels. Includes helper functions and datasets
    for creating choropleth maps, thematic visualizations, and spatial analyses. Boundary data are based on
    Kenya's 47 counties and their constituent sub-counties as defined by the
    Independent Electoral and Boundaries Commission (IEBC).
